abab




You are require to form a palindrome by adding 0 or more characters to the string at any location which you find appropriate. Return the minimum number of 
characters which needs to be added to string to transform it into a palindrom. 

Input
abab

Output
1

Explanation
A palindrome can be obtained by adding an 'a' to the end of the strong to form 'ababa'.

Input
abacaba

Output
0
